      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": ["word_266", "word_267", "word_268", "word_269", "word_270", "word_271", "word_272", "word_273", "word_274", "word_275", "word_276", "word_277", "word_278", "word_279", "word_280", "word_281", "word_282", "word_283", "word_284", "word_285", "word_286", "word_287", "word_288", "word_289"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": ["word_290", "word_291", "word_292", "word_293", "word_294", "word_295", "word_296", "word_297", "word_298", "word_299", "word_300", "word_301", "word_302", "word_303", "word_304", "word_305", "word_306", "word_307", "word_308"]
    },
